description:
PpControlLink:  Table recording characteristics of Point-to-Point control links in a radio access network, including timestamps, cell identifiers, and endpoint IP addresses.

dateTime: Timestamp indicating when the control link data was recorded.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located.
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier (likely a duplicate of CellId).
Id3:  An auxiliary identifier, value is '1' in this sample.
Id4: An auxiliary identifier, value is 'internal' in this sample.
vsDataType: Type of data, indicating this data relates to Point-to-Point control links.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format, specifying Ericsson-specific attributes.
PpControlLink.remoteEndPoint: IP address of the remote endpoint of the control link.
PpControlLink.ppControlLinkId: Identifier for the specific Point-to-Point control link, value is 'internal' in this sample.
PpControlLink.localEndPoint: IP address of the local endpoint of the control link.
